Package: pantheon-shell
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${germinate:Depends}
Recommends: ${germinate:Recommends}
Description: Modern and modular DE-independent desktop shell
 Pantheon Shell is a modern and modular DE-independent desktop shell
 developed by elementary Project.
 .
 This package installs all components of the shell.
 It is also used to help ensure proper upgrades, so it is recommended that
 it not be removed.

Package: pantheon
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${germinate:Depends}
Recommends: ${germinate:Recommends}
Description: Pantheon Desktop Environment
 Pantheon is a desktop environment based on GNOME with a strong focus on user
 experience. It's developed by elementary project.
 .
 This package installs all Pantheon apps that are shipped with the OS by default.
 It is also used to help ensure proper upgrades, so it is recommended that
 it not be removed.

Package: elementary-sdk
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${germinate:Depends}
Recommends: ${germinate:Recommends}
Description: elementary Developer Kit
 Contains recommended packages for developing applications for elementary OS.
